     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>❧Ad authorem Ric. Ma<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>thaeus,
Londoniensis minister.</head>
   <l>TVus probatur à pijs labor bonus:</l>
   <l>Qui quod pium est non diligit,</l>
   <l>Noli put are vincere hunc virum tibi<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>
   </l>
   <l>Huic sit loquela libera.</l>
   <l>Quis Zoilum fugit pius? Tu nec potes:</l>
   <l>Bonis mali nam detrahunt.</l>
   <l>Tibi beata sit precor solatio</l>
   <l>Vita ea, Deus quam tunc dabit,</l>
   <l>Cum tua fides Christo vt facit des obuiam</l>
   <l>Regno patris summi sui.</l>
</div>
